\section desc Description
<!-- Short description of what this package is supposed to provide -->

Classes defining surfaces with or without bounds and related classes.

Surfaces are reference counted: they handle their lifetime themslves,
providing that the proper pointer typedefs are used to handle them.
To enforce this, they should be built using the static build() method. 

